{
  "stem": "20848.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After being three months in Majdanek, and witnessing a terrible lot of atrocities and deaths and horror, they came.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said to you, there were rumors that the Germans are losing the war and the-- that the-- the end is coming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans, as I said, were wearing white bands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, a tank rolled into the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the tank had a white star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was sitting somebody in a different uniform to the SS uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we, the Jewish women-- because we knew the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody was saying look, it's-- it's a foreign tank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We've been liberated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's a foreign tank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we, the Jewish women in camp, said, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We haven't been liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Germans are just staging a show to see how we're going to react.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because that was just exactly what they would do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were these kind of-- of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there were with us Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Uk-- not Jewish women, Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And those who came-- they were very tough and rough women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Ooh, were they tough and rough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was with them in-- in Birkenau, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And what they did-- I don't know how they found a twig, a twig without leaves, just an empty twig.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know where they found it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they ran to the tank.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they handed in the twig to the man who was sitting in the tank.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he took the twig.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we realize there's no shooting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We have been liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So everybody started running to the tank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And on the-- in the tank was sitting this English-- we were liberated by English army-- was sitting this English very high ranking officer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Later-- he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
